# Looking into It

[ link]
|rev2=Pitchfork Media |rev2Score=(7.3/10) [https://web.archive.org/web/20080924123159/http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/article/record_review/145296-all-girl-summer-fun-band-looking-into-it link]}}
Looking Into It is the third album by All Girl Summer Fun Band, released in 2008, and the first to be self-released on the AGSFB Music label.
